---

<div class="bg-white py-12">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="lg:text-center">
      <h2 class="text-base text-forest-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">Why Choose Us</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl text-forest-900 font-serif">
        Comfort in the Wild
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-xl text-gray-500 lg:mx-auto">
        Discover why families have been returning to Davy Crockett Campground for generations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <dl class="space-y-10 md:space-y-0 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-10">
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <dt>
            <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-forest-500 text-white">
              <!-- Heroicon name: outline/home -->
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Premium Cabins</p>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
            From rustic one-room cabins to full luxury lodges with kitchens and hot tubs.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <dt>
            <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-forest-500 text-white">
              <!-- Heroicon name: outline/sparkles -->
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Modern Amenities</p>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
            Heated pool, clean bathhouses, General Store, and free Wi-Fi throughout.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <dt>
            <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-forest-500 text-white">
              <!-- Heroicon name: outline/sun -->
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Family Fun</p>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
            Playgrounds, fishing pond, hiking trails, and seasonal events for kids of all ages.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 4 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <dt>
            <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-forest-500 text-white">
              <!-- Heroicon name: outline/globe-alt -->
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Prime Location</p>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
            Minutes from historical sites, antique shopping, and authentic Tennessee dining.
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
        
    <!-- Optional: Add images below features to show off more -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-10 gap-x-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:gap-x-8">
        <div class="group relative">
            <div class="w-full min-h-80 bg-gray-200 aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3 rounded-md overflow-hidden group-hover:opacity-75 h-64 lg:h-80">
                <img src="/general_store.jpg" alt="General Store" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center lg:w-full lg:h-full">
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 font-bold">General Store on Site</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="group relative">
             <div class="w-full min-h-80 bg-gray-200 aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3 rounded-md overflow-hidden group-hover:opacity-75 h-64 lg:h-80">
                <img src="/lake2.jpg" alt="Fishing on Cherokee Lake" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center lg:w-full lg:h-full">
            </div>
             <h3 class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 font-bold">Fishing & The Lake</h3>
        </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
